        "setup": "Create a PAT in your Tableau account settings as described in [Personal Access Tokens](https://help.tableau.com/current/server/en-us/security_personal_access_tokens.htm). You use the PAT `name` and `secret` with the REST API `signin` method to obtain a temporary credentials token for API calls. For Tableau Cloud with MFA enabled, PATs are required for REST sign-in.",
